quran[30]{c,v,t}:
  21,83,"wadhkr - 'ayuha alrasul - eabdana aywb, 'iidh abtlynah bidurin wsqm eazim fi jsdh, wafaqd 'ahlih wmalh wwldh, fasabr wahtsb, wanadaa rabih eaza wajala 'aniy qad asabny aldr, wa'ant 'arham alrahmyn, fakshfh eny"
  21,84,"fastjbna lah dea'h, warafaena eanh albla', wrddna ealayh ma fqdh min 'ahl wawulid wmal mdaefana, faealna bih dhlk rahmatan mnna, waliakun qudwatan likuli sabir ealaa albla', raj rahmatan rbh, eabid lh"
  21,85,"wadhkr 'iismaeil wa'iidris wadha alkfl, kl hwla' min alsaabirin ealaa taeat allah subhanah wteala, waean measyh, waealaa aqdarh, fasthqu aldhikr balthna' aljmyl"
  21,86,"wadkhlnahm fi rhmtna, 'iinahum mmn salah batinuh wzahrh, fatae allah waeamil bima 'amrih bh"
  21,87,"wadhkur qisat sahib alhwt, wahu yunis bin matta ealayh alslam, 'ursilah allah 'iilaa qawmih fdeahm falam ywmnu, ftweeadhm bialeadhab falam ynybu, walam ysbr ealayhim kama 'amrih allh, wakharaj min baynihim ghadbana elyhm, dayqana sadrah besyanhm, wazana 'ana allah ln ydyiq ealayh wywakhdhh bhdhh almkhalft, fabtlah allah bshdt aldyq walhbs, waltqmh alhut fi albhr, fnada rabih fi zulumat allayl walbahr wbtn alhut taybana metrfana bzlmh; ltrkh alsabr ealaa qwmh, qayla: la 'ilh 'iilaa 'ant sbhank, 'iiniy kunt min alzalmyn"
  21,88,"fastjbna lah dea'h, wkhllasnah min gham hadhih alshdt, wkdhlk nunji almsddiqyn aleamilin bshrena"
  21,89,"wadhkr - 'ayuha alrasul - qisat eabd allah zakariaa hin daea rabah 'ana yrzqh aldhariyat lamaa kabirt snnuh qayla rabi la ttrkny whydana la eaqib ly, hab li warthana yaqum bi'amr aldiyn fi alnaas min bedy, wa'ant khayr albaqin wakhayr man khlfny bkhyr"
  21,90,"fastjbna lah duea'ah wawahabna lah ealaa alkibar aibnih yhya, wajaealna zawjatih salihatan fi akhlaqha wsalht llhml walwladt baed 'an kanat eaqrana, 'iinahum kanuu ybadrwn 'iilaa kl khyr, wayadeunana raghibin fima endna, khayifin min eqwbtna, wakanuu lana khadiein mtwadeyn"
  21,91,"wadhkr - 'ayuha alrasul - qisat maryam aibnat eimran alati hfzt farjaha min alhram, walam tat fahishatan fi hyatha, fa'arsil allah 'iilayha jbryl ealayh alslam, fnfkh fi jayb qmysha, fwslt alnfkht 'iilaa rhmha, fakhalaq allah bdhlk alnfkh almasih eisaa ealayh alslam, fhmlt bih min ghyr zwj, fakanat hi wabnaha bdhlk elamt ealaa qudrat allh, webrt llkhlq 'iilaa qiam alsaet"
  21,92,"hwla' al'anbia' jmyeana dinahum wahd, al'islam, wahu alastslam lilah baltaet w'ifradh balebadt, wallah subhanah wteala rabi alkhalq faebuduh - 'ayuha alnaas - wahdah la sharik lh"
  21,93,"lkn alnaas akhtalafuu ealaa rslhm, wtfrraq kthyr min atbaehm fi aldiyn shyeana wahzabana, febdu almkhlwqyn walahwa', wakuluhum rajieun 'iilayna wmhasbwn ealaa ma felu"
  21,94,"fmn altzm al'iiman biallah wrslh, waeamil ma yastatie min salih al'aemal taetan lilah webadt lah fala yudie allah eamalih wala ybtlh, bal yudaeifh klh adeafana kthyrt, wsyjd ma eamaluh fi kitabah yawm yubeth baed mwth"
  21,95,"wmmtne ela ahl alquraa alati 'ahlaknaha bsbb kufruhum wzlmhm, rjwehm 'iilaa aldunya qabl yawm alqyamt; lystdrku ma frtu fyh"
  21,96,"f'idha futih sadi yajuj wmajwj, wantlqu min murtafaeat al'ard wantshru fi jnbatha msreyn, dana yawm alqiamat wbdat ahwalh fa'iidha 'absar alkufaar min shdt alfazae maftuhatan la takad tatrif, yadeun ealaa 'anfusahum balwyl fi hsrt: ya waylana qad kunaa lahyn ghafilin ean hdha alyawm waean al'iiedad lh, wakunaa bdhlk zalmyn"
  21,97,"f'idha futih sadi yajuj wmajwj, wantlqu min murtafaeat al'ard wantshru fi jnbatha msreyn, dana yawm alqiamat wbdat ahwalh fa'iidha 'absar alkufaar min shdt alfazae maftuhatan la takad tatrif, yadeun ealaa 'anfusahum balwyl fi hsrt: ya waylana qad kunaa lahyn ghafilin ean hdha alyawm waean al'iiedad lh, wakunaa bdhlk zalmyn"
  21,98,"'inkm - 'ayuha alkufaar - wama kuntum taebudun min dun allah min al'asnam wman radi bebadtkm 'iiaah min aljini wal'ins, waqud jahanam whtbha, 'antum wahum fiha dakhlwn"
  21,99,"lw kan hwla' aladhin ebdtmwhm min dun allah taealaa alihatan tastahiqu alebadt ma dakhaluu nar jahanam maeakum 'ayuha almshrkwn, 'inn kla min aleabidin walmebwdyn khalidun fi nar jhnm"
  21,100,"lhwla' almueadhabin fi alnaar alam ynby eanha zfyrhm aldhy tataradad fih anfashm, wahum fi alnaar la ysmewn; min hwl edhabhm"
  21,101,"'iina aladhin sabaqat lahum minaa sabiqat alsaeadat alhasanat fi ealimna bkwnhm min 'ahl aljnt, 'uwlayik ean alnaar mbedwn, fala yadkhulunaha wala yakunun qrybana mnha"
  21,102,"la yasmaeun sawt lhybha wahtraq alajsad fiha faqad sknu manaziluhum fi aljnt, wasbhu fima tashtahih nfwshm min neymha wldhatha muqimin 'iqamtan daymt"
  21,103,"la ykhyfhm alhwl aleazim yawm alqyamt, bal tbshrhm almlaykt: hdha yawmukum aladhi wueidtum fih alkramt min allah wjzyl althwab. yawm natwi alsama' kama tutwa alsahifat ealaa ma kutb fyha, wnbeth fih alkhalq ealaa hayyat khalqna lahum 'awal marat kama wldthm amhathm, dhlk waead allah aladhi la ytkhllaf, waeadna bdhlk wedana hqana elyna, 'iinaa kunaa faeilin daymana ma naeid bh"
  21,104,"la ykhyfhm alhwl aleazim yawm alqyamt, bal tbshrhm almlaykt: hdha yawmukum aladhi wueidtum fih alkramt min allah wjzyl althwab. yawm natwi alsama' kama tutwa alsahifat ealaa ma kutb fyha, wnbeth fih alkhalq ealaa hayyat khalqna lahum 'awal marat kama wldthm amhathm, dhlk waead allah aladhi la ytkhllaf, waeadna bdhlk wedana hqana elyna, 'iinaa kunaa faeilin daymana ma naeid bh"
  21,105,"wlqd katabna fi alkutub almnzlt min baed ma kutib fi allwh almhfwz: 'ana al'ard yarithuha eibad allah alsaalihun aladhin qamuu bima 'umru bh, wajtanibuu maa nuhu enh, wahum 'umat muhamad salaa allah ealayh wslm"
  21,106,'in fi hadha almtlww min almwezt laebrt kafiatan liqawm eabidin allah bima shreh lahum wrdyh mnhm
  21,107,"wma 'arsalnak - 'ayuha alrasul - 'iilaa rahmatan lajamie alnas, faman aman bik saeid wnja, waman lam yumin khab wkhsr"
  21,108,"ql: 'iina aladhi 'uwhy 'ily wbueitht bh: 'ana 'ilhkm aldhy yastahiqu alebadt wahdah hu allh, faslmu lh, wanqadu lebadth"
  21,109,"fa'iin 'aerad hwla' ean al'islam faqul lhm: 'ubalighukum jmyeana maa awhah allah taealaa 'ilya, fa'ana wa'antum mstwwn fi aleilm lmma 'andhartukum whdhrtkm, wlst 'aelam - baed dhlk - mataa yahilu bikum ma wueidtum bih min aledhab?"
  21,110,"'in allah yaelam ma tjhrwn bih min aqwalkm, wama taktumunah fi srayrkm, wsyhasbkm elyh"
  21,111,"wlst 'adri lel takhir aleadhab aldhy astejltmwh astdraj lakum wabtla', wa'ana ttmteu fi aldunya 'iilaa hyn; ltzdadu kfrana, thuma yakun 'aezam leqwbtkm"
  21,112,"qal alnabiu salaa allah ealayh wslm: rbb afsl baynana wabayn qawmina almukadhibin bialqada' alhq. wnsal rabana alrhmn, wnsteyn bih ealaa ma tasifwnh - 'ayuha alkufaar - min alshirk waltkdhyb walaftra' elyh, wama ttwedwna bih min alzuhur walghlbt"